			<div class="content" id="post-content-1223925">
									

<p>Only the interior is indestructible, the exterior is as vulnerable as any standard shipping container. So if his theory is correct, you could remove the majority of the container and the portal would still work. If he's wrong, and the container is a vital piece of the object, the whole thing could go tits up.</p>
